Constructor 

	- is used to intialiaze the objects .
	- special member function .
	- ctor name is same as classname .
	- 2 types of constructor 
		1.default ctor 
		2.parameterised ctor 

	- it automatically calls when you will create an instance / object of that class.

	- it allocate the memory 
	- ctor doesn't have returntype not even void .
	


